# ===== Paper-specific Analysis Scripts =====
# These scripts generate results for paper writing/submission
# They contain sensitive result data and are not part of core BMN method
# 
# GitHub-tracked files:
#   - Core BMN: BMN_DD.py, Decoder_DD.py, scr_exact_bvp_solver.py
#   - Evaluation: evaluate_bmn_random_exact_cases.py, evaluate_decoder_test_exact_cases.py
#   - Comparison baseline: DecoderOptimizationInversion.py
#   - Config: para_config.json, physics_config.json
# ---
analysis_4_2_bmn_inversion_validation.py
analysis_4_2.o*
analysis_4_3_bmn_dataset_size_sensitivity.py
analysis_4_3.o*
analysis_4_3_1_bmn_decoder_dataset_size_sensitivity.py
analysis_4_3_1.o*
analysis_4_5_bmn_sensor_layout_sensitivity.py
analysis_4_5.o*
analysis_4_bmn_sensitivity_utils.py

